#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:486
msgid ""
"Here you are, the outside. Not too different from the last report of some "
"years ago... or centuries, I don't know."
msgstr ""
"Eccoci fuori. NOn è cambiato granché dal nostro ultimo rapporto di qualche "
"anno... o secolo fa, non so."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:487
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Everything is so... dry... There is no plant that could thrive in this heat!"
msgstr ""
"Tutto è così... arido... Non c'è una pianta che possa crescere in questa "
"fornace!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:488
msgid ""
"That is why our people moved to that valley, to protect themselves from "
"death in the desert. Not all of them found the valley, though. We have "
"always wondered what happened to the other group."
msgstr ""
"Ecco perché il nostro popolo ha lasciato questa valle, per scampare alla "
"morte nel deserto. Però non tutti trovarono la valle. Ci siamo sempre "
"chiesti cosa sia successo all'altro gruppo."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:489
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"They could only have died in the desert. The harsh suns and the lack of "
"water and food are peril enough; savage orcs or nomadic human bandits "
"complete the tale."
msgstr ""
"Da quel che so, potrebbero essere morti nel deserto. Se non sono morti per i "
"soli infuocati o la mancanza di cibo e acqua, allora per mano dei luridi "
"orchi selvaggi o dei banditi nomadi."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:490
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I suppose so. But, where are we? The ancient records will have nothing to "
"say of this desert, which was likely a forest before the Fall."
msgstr ""
"Suppongo di sì. Ma, dove siamo? Le antiche esplorazioni non ci servono in "
"questo deserto che potrebbe essere stato una foresta prima della “caduta”."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:491
msgid ""
"If I remember correctly, we are approaching to Longlier, the River of Bones."
msgstr ""
"Se mi ricordo bene, ci stiamo avvicinando a Longlier, il fiume di ossa."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:492
msgid "A river? Great, then we could renew our water supplies there."
msgstr "Un fiume? Magnifico, allora potremo rifornirci di acqua."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:493
msgid ""
"I doubt that. It has been dried up by the suns, and if water remains, it is "
"not pure. Living beings don't last much without water, so you must fill the "
"supplies in this oasis before departing towards Northwest."
msgstr ""
"Ne dubito. È stato prosciugato dal sole e se c'è ancora dell'acuqa non "
"sarebbe pura. Gli esseri viventi non vivono a lungo senza acqua perciò "
"dovrete rifornirvi in questa oasi prima di partire verso nord-ovest."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:494
msgid ""
"Over time, supporting our people will be more difficult, specially here in "
"the desert. Breeding horses for mounts is already impossible for want of "
"fodder."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:495
msgid ""
"Indeed. Let's go. The faster we find better watered country, the better. We "
"cannot stay here for the rest of our lives, there are too many of us."
msgstr ""

#. [event]: (type=Ghost)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:501
msgid "A ghost?"
msgstr "Un fantasma?"

#. [event]: (type=Ghost)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:502
msgid "It seems hostile. Mal Keshar, can you do anything about it?"
msgstr "Sembra ostile. Mal Keshar, puoi fare qualcosa?"

#. [event]: (type=Ghost)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:503
msgid ""
"No. These ghosts have free will, and roam about these sands due to their "
"sudden death."
msgstr ""
"No. Questi fantasmi hanno una propria volontà e vagano per queste sabbie a "
"causa dalla loro morte improvvisa."

#. [event]: (type=Ghost)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:504
msgid "What kind of death?"
msgstr "Come sono morti?"

#. [event]: (type=Ghost)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:505
msgid ""
"Crushed alive by their own houses, rocks, mountains... This is what was left "
"of the Empire of Wesnoth after the cataclysm when the third sun, Gaia, fell "
"over the land."
msgstr ""
"Schiacciati vivi dalle loro proprie case, da rocce, montagne... Questo è "
"quello che rimane dell'impero di Wesnoth dopo il cataclisma quando il terzo "
"sole, Gaia, cadde sulla terra."

#. [event]: (type=Ghost)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:506
msgid "A third sun? How could that happen..."
msgstr "Un terzo sole? Come potrebbe essere..."

#. [event]: (type=Ghost)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:507
msgid ""
"(sighs) Galas, again, it is something that you should not, nor would ever "
"need to know."
msgstr ""
"(sospira) Galas, anche questo è una cosa che tu non avresti dovuto né voluto "
"mai aver bisongo di sapere."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:514
msgid "Hey you!"
msgstr "Ehi voi!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:515
msgid "Oops. Just what we needed..."
msgstr "Ops. Proprio quello che ci serviva..."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:516
msgid "Travelers, wait. I come in peace."
msgstr "Viaggiatori, aspettate. Io vengo in pace."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:517
msgid "Huh? Speak."
msgstr "Eh? Parla."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:518
msgid ""
"If you want to come to our village to replenish your supplies, you'll have "
"to pay us a small fee."
msgstr ""
"Se volete venirenei nostri villaggi per rifornirvi, dovrete pagare un "
"piccolo obolo."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:519
msgid "And how much would it be?"
msgstr "E quanto sarebbe?"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:520
msgid "$fee_value| pieces of gold."
msgstr "$fee_value| pezzi d'oro."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:521
msgid "Um... we'll think about it later."
msgstr "Mh... ci rifletterò più tardi."

#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:546
msgid "Hey, travelers!"
msgstr "Ehi, viaggiaori!"

#. [event]
#. [event]: (type=Tux)}
#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:721
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:139
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:105
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:547
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Huh?"

#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:548
msgid ""
"I'd recommend you not to head south-west. The Loyalists occupy a vast "
"territory in that direction, and it is said that in the frontier mountains, "
"those that you see close to you, strange things happen and can be seen at "
"night."
msgstr ""

#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:549
msgid ""
"Thanks for the tip. But, why don't you abandon this oasis then? There are "
"others further to the north and east."
msgstr ""

#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:550
msgid ""
"Because most of them are controled by orcs or hostile savages. We don't have "
"the forces to fight them yet, so we prefer to struggle for surviving in this "
"small valley where we know exactly what threathens our lives."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:569
msgid ""
"Will you pay us before entering the village, wanderers? It's $fee_value| "
"pieces of gold."
msgstr ""
"Ci pagherete prima di entrare nel villaggio, viaggiatori? Sono $fee_value| "
"pezzi d'oro.."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#. [event]
#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/05a_Crossfire.cfg:241
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:572
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1328
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/08a_Errand_of_Hope.cfg:573
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/08a_Errand_of_Hope.cfg:1166
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/08a_Errand_of_Hope.cfg:1202
msgid "Um..."
msgstr "Ehm..."

#. [option]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:574
msgid "Yes. Here is the gold."
msgstr "Sì. Ecco l'oro."

#. [command]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:584
msgid ""
"You are welcome, then. As long as you don't start pillaging our village, "
"that is. Know that if you do so, you'll encounter only problems."
msgstr ""
"Siete i benvenuti, allora. Finché non inizierete a razziare il nostro "
"villaggio, si intende. Sappiate che se lo farete, avrete solo problemi."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:596
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:657
msgid "Hey, they are invading our houses! It's a hostile assault!"
msgstr "Ehi, invadono le nostre case! È un attacco ostile!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:597
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:658
#, fuzzy
msgid "I warned you, strangers. We'll have to end you now."
msgstr "Vi avevo avvertito, stranieri. Adesso dovremo liberarci di voi."

#. [option]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:608
msgid "No. We may get better results if we take over your village"
msgstr ""

#. [command]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:614
#, fuzzy
msgid "Very well, then. You have asked for it."
msgstr "Benissimo, allora. Lo avete voluto voi."

#. [option]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:624
msgid "No, unfortunately we don't have that much gold."
msgstr "No, purtroppo non abbiamo così tanto oro."

#. [command]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:630
#, fuzzy
msgid "All right, then. You have asked for it."
msgstr "Benissimo, allora. Lo avete voluto voi."

#. [option]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:640
msgid ""
"Oh, please. Have mercy on us! We were forced to abandon our home, and are "
"now lost in this vast desert! How can you expect us to have enough gold to "
"give you?"
msgstr ""
"Oh, vi prego. Abbiate pietà di noi! Siamo stati costretti ad abbandonare la "
"nostra patria e pra siamo sperduti in questo deserto così vasto! Come potete "
"pensare che abbiamo abbastanza ora da darvi?"

#. [command]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:646
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Um... Very well. You may pass this time. But don't expect me to be merciful "
"a second time! And no pillaging our village. Know that if you do so, you'll "
"encounter only trouble."
msgstr ""
"Em... va bene. Questa volta potete passare. Ma non aspettatevi che io sia "
"pietoso una seconda volta! E farete meglio a non razziare il nostro "
"villaggio. Sappiate che se lo farete, avrete solo problemi."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:687
msgid "Ah? Elves? I must be hallucinating again..."
msgstr "Eh? Elfi? Ho di nuovo le traveggole..."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:692
msgid "This doesn't look good..."
msgstr "Non è una bella situazione..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:697
msgid ""
"But I never had hallucinations that could speak. Intruders! And they are "
"elves! Go get'em!"
msgstr ""
"Ma non ho avuto delle allucinazioni parlanti. Intrusi! E sono elfi! "
"Prendiamoli!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:702
msgid ""
"Anyone who dares oppose us shall perish, does not matter if it's orc or "
"human."
msgstr "Chi osa oporsi a noi morirà, non importa che sia un orco o un uomo."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:707
msgid "Orcs... good. It has been a long time since I defeated one myself!"
msgstr ""
"Orchi... bene. È passato molto tempo da quando ne ho eliminato uno con le "
"mie mani!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:712
msgid ""
"We could ignore them and continue our journey, but I'm not sure if it would "
"be a good idea."
msgstr ""
"Potremmo ignorarli e continuare il nostro viaggio, ma non sono sicuro che "
"sarebbe una buona idea."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:749
msgid "Undead! Everyone, to arms! It's an invasion!"
msgstr "Non-morti! Tutti alle armi! È un'invasione!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:754
msgid ""
"Somebody should catch that idiot and cut his tongue. Now that he has given "
"alarm to his friends we'll have to deal with them!"
msgstr ""
"Qualcuno dovrebbe prendere questo idiota e tagliarli la lingua. Adesso che "
"ha dato l'allarme ai suoi amici, dovremo affrontarli!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:788
msgid "Ah? What is that thing?"
msgstr "Eh? Cos'è questa cosa?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:795
msgid ""
"Scorpions, inhabitants of the sands. Beware, their tail has a poisonous "
"sting that could tresspass your heart in a second."
msgstr ""
"Scorpioni, abitatori delle sabbie. Fate attezione, la coda ha un pungiglione "
"velenoso che potrebbe trapassarvi il cuore in un attimo."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:814
msgid "Rooaargh!!"
msgstr "Rooaargh!!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:819
msgid ""
"I have seen odd things in my life, but that is just ridiculous! A crawling "
"glob of mud?"
msgstr ""
"Ne ho viste di cose strane in vita mia, ma questo è solo ridicolo! Un "
"mucchio di fango strisciante?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:824
msgid ""
"Crawling yes, but it is not a simple glob of mud, but one animated by magic "
"means. Although they are not specially tough, if you get surrounded by a "
"pack of them you will have serious trouble."
msgstr ""
"È vero che striscia, ma non è solo un mucchio di fango, ma è stato animato "
"con la magia. Anche se non particolarmente resistente, se foste circondati "
"da un gruppo di questi saresti in guai seri."

#. [scenario]: id=04_Over_the_Sands
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:834
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:837
msgid "Hunting Troll"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: race=troll
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:862
msgid "Me thinks hungry be. Elves be tasty, yes. Tasty will eaten be."
msgstr "Io penso fame ho. Elfi gustosi sono, sì. Gustosi mangiati voglio."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:867
msgid "I don't really think I taste good. Uh-oh."
msgstr "Non penso di essere gustoso, io. Oh-oh."

#. [message]: race=troll
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:899
msgid "Aaah, undeady! I crack you will do!"
msgstr "Aaah, non-morto! A pezzi ti farò!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:904
msgid "We'll see about that."
msgstr "Lo vedremo."

#. [unit]: type=Huntsman, id=Glen
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:933
msgid "Glen"
msgstr "Glen"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:946
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:947
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:948
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:949
msgid "Outlaw ambusher"
msgstr "Fuorilegge imboscatore"

#. [message]: role=filthy
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:967
msgid "Ha, ha, ha! We got you! There is no escapatory now!"
msgstr "Ah ah ah! Presi! Adesso siete in trappola!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:992
msgid "Aaah! Yelp!"
msgstr "Aaah! Aiuto!"

#. [message]: role=filthy
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1007
msgid ""
"Hey, wait, is that an elf? I thought they were long gone from the face of "
"earth!"
msgstr ""
"Ehi, aspetta, è un elfo? Pensavo che fossero scomparsi dalla faccia della "
"terra!"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1016
msgid ""
"I did too, but it seems these pointy-eared demons are impossible to get rid "
"of."
msgstr ""
"Lo pensavo anche io, ma pare che sia impossibile liberarsi di questo demoni "
"con le orecchie a punta."

#. [message]: role=filthy
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1021
msgid "It matters little now. Kill it!"
msgstr "Poco importa. Uccidilo!"

#. [message]: role=filthy
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1048
msgid "Undead! These damned abominations pursue us again!"
msgstr "Non-morti! Questi dannati abominii ci inseguono di nuovo!"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1056
msgid "Then we'll have to get rid of them once for all."
msgstr "Allora dobbiamo liberarcene una volta per tutte."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1065
msgid ""
"They are blocking our path to the north west following the river's stream. "
"We must defeat them before continuing."
msgstr ""
"Stanno bloccando il nostro percorso verso nord-ovest lungo la corrente del "
"fiume. Dobbiamo sconfiggerli prima di continuare."

#. [objectives]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1071
msgid "Defeat the leader of the bandits who control the north-western area"
msgstr ""
"Sconfiggi il comandante dei banditi che controllano la regione nord-ovest"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1091
msgid "Ouch! Puny weakling, you won't beat meee..."
msgstr "Acc! Meschini smidollati, non mi sconfiggereteee..."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1096
msgid "Uh... looks like I did."
msgstr "Ah... pare che l'abbiamo fatto."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1101
msgid ""
"These bandits seem to have accumulated some gold. It's not a great amount, "
"but it will do for our needs."
msgstr ""
"Pare che questi banditi abbiano accumulato dell'oro. Non è molto, ma ci "
"servirà."

#. [objectives]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1110
msgid ""
"Galas, Anlindë or Mal Keshar must reach the North-west border of the map"
msgstr ""
"Galas, Anlindë o Mal Keshar devono raggiungere il bordo nord-ovest della "
"mappa"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1128
msgid "Argh! I'm vanquished!"
msgstr "Argh! Sono stato sconfitto!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1133
msgid ""
"This orc kept some gold in his tent. These must be difficult times for them, "
"since it is not more than a few dozens, but it is better than nothing."
msgstr ""
"Questo orco custodiva dell'oro in questa tenda. Pare fossero tempi difficili "
"per loro datoche sono solo poche decine di pezzi, ma è meglio di niente."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1174
msgid "The river's bottom carves a canyon to the northwest."
msgstr "Il fondo del fiume scava un canalone a nord-ovest."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1179
msgid ""
"We must follow it from outside, for I don't know how it goes up to the "
"mountains."
msgstr "Dobbiamo seguire all'aperto perché non so come scalare le montagne."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1187
msgid "We can't continue before defeating these bandits first!"
msgstr "Non possiamo proseguire prima di aver sconfitto questi banditi!"

#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1205
msgid ""
"Something disturbs me. These sand dwellers talk about our race like if they "
"had met us recently. After all these centuries, shouldn't they have at least "
"forgotten our name?"
msgstr ""
"C'è qualcosa che non va. Questi abitatori delle sabbie parlavano della "
"nostra razza come se ci avessero incontrato di recente. Dopo tutti questi "
"secoli, non dovrebbero aver dimenticato almeno il nostro nome?"

#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1206
msgid ""
"I think so, and I wonder too what they meant. But anyway, we should not let "
"small questions such as this delay us any further. We have a mission to "
"complete, and time is critical for it."
msgstr ""
"Lo penso anche io e mi domando cosa volevano dire con quel discorso. "
"Tuttavia, non possiamo permettere che i dettagli ci ritardino ulteriormente. "
"Abbiamo un compito da portare a termine e il tempo è critico."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1234
msgid ""
"Come back to this world, from your eternal dream of battles, elvish hero of "
"long past times! I call upon you!"
msgstr ""
"Torna in questo mondo, dai tuoi eterni sogni di battaglia, eroe degli elfi "
"dei tempi remoti! Io ti invoco!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1249
msgid "At your orders, masters!"
msgstr "Ai vostri ordini, padroni!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1250
msgid ""
"But, but, it's an elven warrior! Quite pale and... translucid, though. What "
"is this, Mal Keshar?"
msgstr ""
"Ma, ma, è un elfo guerriero! Un po' troppo pallido... e trasparente, però. "
"Cos'è, Mal Keshar?"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1251
msgid ""
"This, my 'friend', is a he, one of your kinsmen. In contrast with most of my "
"minions, this elvish spirit does not fight unwillingly; he has been "
"following you all this time, and whilst not having the power to materialize "
"by himself, he has been waiting for the oportunity to fight for you once "
"again; he just needed a little help from an expert like me."
msgstr ""
"Questo, mio «amico», è uno della vostra razza. A differenza della maggior "
"parte dei miei servi, questo spirito elfico non combatte contro la sua "
"volontà; per tutto questo tempo vi ha seguiti e, dato che non aveva il "
"potere di materializzarsi da solo, stava aspettando l'opportunità per "
"combattere con voi ancora una volta; aveva solo bisogno di un po' di aiuto "
"da un esperto come me."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1252
msgid "Are you saying that he has his own will, then?"
msgstr "Stai dicendo, dunque, che è dotato di volontà propria?"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1253
msgid ""
"Exactly. Note that these spirits are stronger and deadlier when fighting in "
"forests; unfortunately, I'm not sure whether there are any left for this "
"purpose."
msgstr ""
"Esattamente. Notate che questi spiriti sono più forti e letali quando "
"combattono nelle foreste; purtroppo, non so se ce ne sono rimasti altri per "
"questi fini."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1269
msgid ""
"(shakes head) I see it and don't believe it... undead fighting for our cause."
msgstr ""
"(scuotendo la testa) Lo vedo e non ci credo... non-morti che combattono per "
"la nostra causa."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1270
msgid "At some point you'll get accustomed to that."
msgstr "A un certo punto ci farai l'abitudine."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1291
msgid ""
"If my memory serves, that path leads to an old mountain pass, that goes high "
"over the ground, yet the height of the surrounding peaks does not allow "
"sunlight to illuminate it most of the time."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1298
msgid "Yes, but remember what the outlaw told us about these mountains."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1302
msgid ""
"If I didn't see her eyes at that moment, I'd not trust those words. However, "
"given that I did, I'm sure she was not lying."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1306
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1324
msgid ""
"Think about it. We would not have to travel through the heat of the desert. "
"That is, at least for me, a great point in favor of it. There should even be "
"more water sources in it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1310
msgid "Um... difficult decission to make."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1316
msgid "Is that good?"
msgstr "È bene?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1320
msgid ""
"The darkness of it probably grants shelter to many foes. I'd prefer to avoid "
"it if possible."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1353
msgid "So, what do you choose, Galas: should we go this way or not?"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:299
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1357
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/19_Legend_of_Wesmere.cfg:297
msgid "Uh..."
msgstr "Eh..."

#. [option]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1359
msgid "Yes, let's go through the mountain pass."
msgstr ""

#. [option]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1366
msgid "No. Perhaps later, if I change my mind."
msgstr ""

#. [command]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1368
msgid "Very well, but I don't think that we could come back later..."
msgstr ""

