msgstr "Elfi? Traditori, andatevene ora o vi uccideremo!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/08a_Errand_of_Hope.cfg:542
msgid "Undead! Begone creepy one, or we crush you!"
msgstr "Non-morto! Vattene mostro raccappricciante o ti schiacceremo!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/08a_Errand_of_Hope.cfg:556
msgid "Ugh. Dis harms a lot..."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/08a_Errand_of_Hope.cfg:570
msgid ""
"Is it really necessary to do this? Kill every foe we stumble upon... "
"shouldn't there be another way?"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/08a_Errand_of_Hope.cfg:571
msgid ""
"Boy, you don't need to see it as an assassination. Just think of it as the "
"evolution of that poor useless beast into a powerful force that can serve us."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/08a_Errand_of_Hope.cfg:572
