msgstr "Argh!! Ah..."

#. [event]: (id=Mal Keshar)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/10_The_Source_of_Light.cfg:1126
msgid "Woses in this place? How odd."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: type=Wose
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/10_The_Source_of_Light.cfg:1130
msgid "Destroy the necromancer!!"
msgstr "Distruggete il necromante!!"

#. [event]: (id=Mal Keshar)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/10_The_Source_of_Light.cfg:1132
#, fuzzy
msgid "Huh? Nay. Prepare to meet your fate, you..."
msgstr "Eh? Preparatevi ad affrontare il vostro destino, vi..."

#. [event]: (id=Mal Keshar)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/10_The_Source_of_Light.cfg:1133
msgid "Stop, we are the Elves of the Valley of Elynia, you must let us pass!"
msgstr ""
"Fermi, siamo gli elfi della valle di Elynia, ci dovete lasciar passare!"

#. [message]: type=Wose
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/10_The_Source_of_Light.cfg:1136
msgid ""
"The elvish race was extinguished by the events after the Fall. You cannot be "
"elves. Impostors!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]: (id=Mal Keshar)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/10_The_Source_of_Light.cfg:1138
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I call upon the powers of Light! May it awake our savior from her millenary "
"sleep!"
msgstr ""
"Io invoco la luce di Eloh! Possa svegliare la nostra sapiente dal suo sonno "
"millenario!"

#. [event]: (id=Mal Keshar)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/10_The_Source_of_Light.cfg:1147
msgid ""
"As Anlindë pronounced the spell, the great tree at the center of the chamber "
"disappeared, and a beautiful elven lady materialized in its place, laying in "
"the grass floor. Big dragonfly wings on her back, her pale red hair and "
"eyes, made it obvious that she was not any elf, but the Lady of Light. Half-"
"asleep, her powers were still enough to illuminate the surroundings without "
"requiring any minimal effort from her."
msgstr ""
"Mentre Anlindë pronunciava l'incantesimo, il grande albero al centro della "
"camera scomparve e al suo posto si materializzò una bellissima signora elfa "
"che giaceva sull'erba. Per le grandi ali di libellula sulla schiena, i "
"chiari capelli rossi, era ovvio che non fosse un elfa, ma la signora della "
"luce. Mezza addormentata i suoi poteri non erano ancora sufficienti per "
"illuminare intorno a lei senza richiedere un minimo sforzo cosciente."

