"Distraeteli, ci serve del tempo prima che il signore della guerra arrivi a "
"finirli!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:316
msgid "En garde, elf!"
msgstr "In guardia, elfo!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:317
msgid ""
"I have not the slightest idea of what they are ranting about, but for me it "
"seems they are guarding that door..."
msgstr ""
"Non ho la minima idea di quello che stai sbraitando, ma secondo me stanno "
"sorvegliando quella porta..."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:323
msgid "Ha, obviously it's an important one. Get out of our path, vermins!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, naturalmente deve essere importante. Toglietevi dal nostro cammino, "
"parassiti!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:324
msgid "You shall not pass!"
msgstr "Non passerete!"

#. [unit]: type=Chaos Warlord, id=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:354
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:692
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:23
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:64
msgid "Elyssa"
msgstr "Elyssa"

#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:372
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Galas, the elvish leader. You have no idea how much time I have been waiting "
"for this moment, to see your face of terror and squash you like a bug, to "
"squash you in the same manner the witch did with me."
msgstr ""
"Galas, tu, capo degli elfi. Non hai idea di quanto tempo ho aspettato questo "
"momento per vedere il tuo viso terrorizzato e schiacciarti come un insetto, "
"schiacciarti nella stesso modo in cui la strega ha fatto con me."

#. [then]
#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:373
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:43
msgid ""
"So you are the monster that killed Anlindë. You shall pay for that, and I'll "
"make sure that no part of your body is left this time to resurrect you!"
msgstr ""
"Dunque sei tu il mostro che ha ucciso Anlindë. Pagherai per questo e mi "
"assicurerò che non rimanga nemmeno una parte del tuo corpo per risuscitarti!"

#. [then]
#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:374
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:44
msgid ""
"Fool, there is no weapon or magical power left in this world to destruct me "
"permanently. You will be only wasting your last minutes of life!"
msgstr ""
"Sciocco, in questo modo non è rimasta arma né potere magico che possa "
"distruggermi permanentemente. Stai solo sprecando gli ultimi tuoi istanti di "
"vita!"

#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:375
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"No, we will prevail. You are the one who will waste her last minutes of life."
msgstr ""
"No, noi vinceremo. Sei tu che stai sprecando gli ultimi istanti della tua "
"vita."

#. [then]
#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:376
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:46
msgid ""
"Ah, the so feared Lady of Light... you are nothing but a girl. I'll teach "
"you a lesson, to respect those who are actually powerful, to respect the "
"lords of Chaos!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, la temuta signora della luce... sei solo una ragazza. Ti darò una "
"lezione, ti insegnerò a rispettare quelli che sono davvero potenti, a "
"rispettare i signori del caos!"

#. [objectives]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:379
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:50
msgid "Defeat the Chaos Warlord"
msgstr "Sconfiggi i il signore della guerra del caos"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:398
msgid "Long live the Machine!"
msgstr "Lunga vita alla macchina!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:418
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:103
msgid ""
"We, the Argazar people, fiddled perilously with the pillars of all "
"lifeforms. And we created unspeakable abominations, that we were forced to "
"enhance and mass-produce, as we were losing a war with the planet Rythé."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:419
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:104
msgid ""
"Those were the Shaxthals. With our knowledge of magic, genetics and "
"technology combinated, we could select the best characteristics of every "
"natural lifeform, add them great strength and resistance, and join them "
"together in a single, new lifeform. The Biomechanicals, or 'Shaxthals', "
"which in our ancient tongue meant 'invincibles'."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:420
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:105
msgid ""
"However, a cataclysm destroyed all our civilization and creations, except "
"for a few of us who survived long enough to set a secret city underground."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:421
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:106
msgid "The Rythenians thought we were gone."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:422
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:107
msgid "But the Shaxthals had their own survival system."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:423
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:108
msgid ""
"Probably most of the biomechanicals that were in the planet's surface during "
"the cataclysm were destroyed, but a small number of them could survive with "
"us underground. However, we forgot an important detail: their instincts."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:424
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:109
msgid ""
"Their instincts prevailed, and commanded them to start consuming our "
"civilization. To take our bodies and integrate them into their own lifeform. "
"For they had an advanced assimilation system that allowed them to integrate "
"into new environments, or adapt them to suit their needs."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:425
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:110
msgid ""
"Not sole environments, but their organisms too. The Shaxthals had the same "
"knowledge of technology we had, but not the knowledge of genetics or magic. "
"Yet, that was more than enough to convert our comrades into mindless "
"servants of their 'system'."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:426
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:111
msgid ""
"Although we tried to make sure their hive could not grow bigger, we noticed "
"that they had developed their own means of reproduction. Their numbers were "
"increasing quickly."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:427
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:112
msgid ""
"With barely a few dozen of us left, we figured out a way to destroy the "
"Shaxthals. The strongest ones, few though, survived. And our lores decided "
"to keep them in cryogenic pods instead of destructing them forever, as they "
"thought they could still be our last hope of survival."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:428
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:113
msgid ""
"But we eventually disappeared. We, as animals, got to a dead end, with no "
"means of reproduction. Our attempts to reproduce our species in a similar "
"way to that of the Shaxthals were futile."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:429
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:114
msgid ""
"Only our knowledge survived, in the form of these glyphs. And in the form of "
"the pods that contained the remaining Shaxthals."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:430
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:115
msgid ""
"We hope with all our might that all this knowledge, technology and history, "
"are not used for bad purposes."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:432
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:116
msgid "That's one heck of a history, that I still have to digest."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:433
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:117
msgid "Really? Do you have a stomach in there?"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:434
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:118
msgid ""
"I guess this explains the strange lifeforms we have found in here. Then, "
"someone unleashed these creatures from their container pods."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:435
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:119
msgid ""
"I think that whoever did that should have been smart enough to have read "
"this story, right? That means he or she did it on purpose. Perhaps it would "
"have been better if that person had been assimilated by these creatures too."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:436
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:120
msgid "Well, perhaps they were assimilated already."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:592
#, fuzzy
msgid "Uh? No! It is... it is impossible! The Union has been summoned!"
msgstr "Eh? No! Non... non è possibile! L'unione!"

#. [objectives]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:596
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:352
msgid "Use the 'Union' attack of Elynia or Mal Keshar to vanquish the Warlord"
msgstr ""
"Usa l'attacco “unione” di Elynia o Mal Keshar per sconfiggere il signore "
"della guerra"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:607
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:238
msgid "Protect them!"
msgstr "Proteggeteli!"

#. [objectives]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:611
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:243
msgid ""
"Distract the Warlord for two turns, during which Elynia and Mal Keshar will "
"not be able to move or attack"
msgstr ""
"Distrai il signore della guerra per due turni durante i quali Elynia e Mal "
"Keshar non saranno in grado di muoversi o attaccare"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:661
#, fuzzy
msgid "Forgive me, Master..."
msgstr "Nooooo... perdonatemi, padrone..."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:662
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:146
msgid "Wait a moment, who are you? Where does your master hide?"
msgstr "Un momento, chi sei? Dove si nasconde il tuo padrone?"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:663
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:147
msgid "I'm not telling you... anything..."
msgstr "Non vi dirò... niente..."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:664
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:148
msgid "No, you actually will tell me. Who are you?"
msgstr "No, tu parlerai invece. Chi sei?"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:665
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:149
msgid "Elynia? What are you doing?"
msgstr "Elynia? Cosa stai facendo?"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:666
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:150
msgid ""
"I am Elyssa, and used to be a wanderer mage before stumbling upon the Empire "
"and the powers of Chaos. The Shadow Master... he taught me things that you "
"cannot imagine. He showed me the powers of the grand Uria! He... they, they "
"converted me to their side, turning me into a demon..."
msgstr ""
"Sono Elyssa ed ero una maga errante prima di incappare nell'impero e nei "
"poteri del caos. Il signore dell'ombra... mi ha insegnato cose che non "
"potete nemmeno immaginare. Mi ha mostrato i poteri del grande Uria! Egli... "
"loro, loro mi hanno convertito alla loro parte, trasformandomi in un "
"demone..."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:667
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:151
msgid "Where does your master hide?"
msgstr "Dove si nasconde il tuo padrone?"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:668
msgid ""
"The Halls of the Damned... the door behind, and the Dark Hive... follow the "
"dark road, and you will find him, in a chamber plenty of his creations..."
msgstr ""
"Le sale dei dannati... la porta dietro e l'alveare nero... segui la strada "
"oscura e lo troverai in una stanza piena delle sue creazioni..."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:669
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:160
msgid "Now you can pass in peace, Elyssa."
msgstr "Ora puoi trapassare in pace, Elyssa."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:670
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:161
msgid ""
"As Elyssa performed her last breathe, her former appearance returned, "
"showing that of a beautiful red-haired human mage."
msgstr ""
"Esalato l'ultimo respiro, Elyssa recuperò il suo aspetto originale di una "
"affascinante maga dai capelli rossi."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:671
msgid ""
"But the group could not rest even for a while, nor give the poor victim a "
"proper burial. So they threw her still warm corpse to the lava to be "
"completely consumed, and purposefully headed towards the Halls of the "
"Damned..."
msgstr ""
"Ma il gruppo non potè riposare nemmeno per un momento, né dare alla "
"disgraziata vittima un'adeguata sepoltura. Perciò gettarono il suo corpo "
"ancora caldo nella lava che lo consumò completamente e si diressero con "
"decisione verso le sale dei dannati..."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:712
msgid "I told you so, fools. I am immortal!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:713
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If any of you can't think of a good idea, this is surely our end! Our backs "
"are surrounded by lava, and it seems that no matter what we try, we won't "
"defeat her!"
msgstr ""
"Se non ti viene in mente nessuna buona idea, questa è davvero al nostra "
"fine! Alle spalle siamo circondati dalla lava e questo bastardo è immortale "
"o qualcosa del genere."

#. [event]
#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:714
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:98
msgid "I have an idea."
msgstr "Ho un'idea."

#. [event]
#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:715
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:99
msgid "What would it be?"
msgstr "Cosa sarebbe?"

#. [event]
#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:716
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:100
msgid "It is highly risky, and I'll need Malin's help. Malin?"
msgstr "È un grosso rischio e mi servirà l'aiuto di Malin. Malin?"

#. [event]
#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:717
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:101
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr "Sì?"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:718
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We need to put our hands together and concentrate. We will try to call upon "
"the power of the Union."
msgstr ""
"Dobbiamo unire le nostre mani e concentrarci. Invocheremo il potere "
"dell'unione."

#. [event]
#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:719
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:103
msgid "We will WHAT?!"
msgstr "Noi faremo COSA?"

#. [event]
#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:720
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:104
msgid "You what?"
msgstr "Tu cosa?"

#. [event]
#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:722
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:106
msgid ""
"The heat must have affected your mind, that is sheer madness. You can't call "
"upon that high power without the help of the Master of Darkness. Attempting "
"to do so could destroy us all!"
msgstr ""
"Il caldo deve averti dato alla testa, è una follia bella e buona. Non puoi "
"invocare questo supremo potere senza l'aiuto del signore dell'oscurità. "
"tentare una cosa del genere ci distruggerà tutti!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:723
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I know, but hasty situations require hasty decissions. Just do as I said and "
"let's hope that it will not fail to us."
msgstr ""
"Lo so, ma nelle situazioni pericolose servono decisioni pericolose. Fa' come "
"ho detto e fidati di me che non succederà niente di male."

#. [event]
#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:724
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:108
msgid "Very well, then..."
msgstr "Benissimo allora..."

#. [event]
#. [then]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:725
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:109
msgid "Let's distract the Warlord in the mean time, then!"
msgstr "Allora, nel frattempo distraiamo il signore della guerra!"

#. [objectives]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:729
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:113
msgid "Move Elynia and Mal Keshar so that they are in adjacent hexes"
msgstr ""
"Sposta Elynia e Mal Keshar in modo che si trovino su esagoni adiacenti."

#. [objectives]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Gauntlet.cfg:730
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/encounter_elyssa.cfg:114
msgid "Distract the Warlord"
msgstr "Distrai il signore della guerra"

#. [scenario]: id=22C_The_Backyard
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard.cfg:7
msgid "The Backyard"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=23A_Interim
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Interim.cfg:40
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:3
msgid "The Dark Hive"
msgstr "L'alveare nero"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Just what we needed. The only possible path goes through the home of those "
"abominable creatures."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:24
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The place stinks with the stench of death and decay. Something seriously "
"evil goes on in this... warren? Hive? Thing?"
msgstr ""
"Questo luogo puzza di morte e putrefazione. Qualcosa di davvero malvagio "
"accade in questo... formicaio? alveare? cosa?"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Let's keep together. It is the only way to protect ourselves against a "
"possible ambush by a swarm of them."
msgstr ""

#. [event]: (type=Tux)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:134
msgid "What is that? Malin, look! I've never seen any creature like that."
msgstr ""

#. [event]: (type=Tux)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:135
msgid "Neither have I. We'd better get out of this tunnel..."
msgstr ""

#. [event]: (type=Tux)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:136
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hey, you! How did you get here?"
msgstr "Un goblin? Come hai fatto ad arrivare qua?"

#. [event]: (type=Tux)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:137
msgid ""
"We don't really know. We found a small crack in the cave wall and a force "
"brought us to this passage."
msgstr ""

#. [event]: (type=Tux)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:138
msgid ""
"Well, no one should be here. I run the game from this place; if anyone found "
"out about me, the world of Wesnoth could be transformed by the evil ones, or "
"even destroyed!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]: (type=Tux)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:140
msgid ""
"(breaths deeply) All right, maybe I got too nervous. Do you want to come in? "
"I was just going to make some cookies for tea-time..."
msgstr ""

#. [event]: (type=Tux)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:141
msgid ""
"Eh, no, sorry bird, but we have a very important mission to accomplish right "
"now. Perhaps later."
msgstr ""

#. [event]: (type=Tux)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:142
msgid ""
"The passage is blocked, you cannot go out unless... unless you promise me to "
"keep this conversation in secret. No, better, pretend that we never met each "
"other."
msgstr ""

#. [event]: (type=Tux)}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22C_The_Backyard/dark_hive_west.cfg:143
#, fuzzy
msgid "We promise..."
