#. [objectives]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Welcome_to_the_Lair/chimera_fight.cfg:26
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Welcome_to_the_Lair/chimera_fight.cfg:53
