msgstr "Arnesius"

#. [side]: type=Aragwaith Slayer, id=Delarel
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/cutscenes/16x.cfg:95
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/cutscenes/14x_B.cfg:100
