"At the zenith of their career, mounted soldiers of Chaos go through unknown "
"rituals and are ascended to the top of the hiearchy. They seem to have "
"become, as their mounts, living, blood-thirsty killer machines. Although "
"just respectable soldiers on their own, a few groups of Cataphracts at night "
"are certainly enough to take over a large town."
msgstr ""

