#. [race]: id=spirit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/spirits.cfg:8
msgid ""
"Natural spirits are rarely seen in mundane places, although it is rumored "
"that they can only be, either summoned by magi, or protecting a great secret "
"of nature."
msgstr ""

